linguine (0.4.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Added a (very rudimentary) widget-mode; this will display one audio or video source, which can be played by clicking the icon.  Updates every half hour.
  * Added Deutche Welle text news rss feed.
  * Fixed a few RSS parser bugs.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Sat, 14 Feb 2015 10:57:38 -0500

linguine (0.3.1) unstable; urgency=low
  * Native Linguine feed display now shows feed name and timestamp.
  * Feeds are also now sorted by name.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Sat, 16 Aug 2014 11:18:44 -0400

linguine (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * New "Feed Source Selection" window added.
  * Adds "The Old Reader" as a source for newsfeeds.  (Support for "The Old Reader" features is still limited.)
  * Ability to suppress display of images in a newsfeed, via a new entry in the Preferences panel.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Wed, 13 Aug 2014 21:03:48 -0400

linguine (0.2.4) unstable; urgency=low
  * Collections of feeds can now be defined in the newsfeeds xml file.
  * Each newsfeed can now be given an arbitrary number of user-defined tags; these tags can then be used when creating collections.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Wed, 06 Aug 2014 19:21:07 -0400

